{"word":"H4069 - מַדּוּעַ - maddûwaʻ - mad-doo'-ah - How","slug":"H4069","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מַדּוּעַ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>maddûwaʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mad-doo'-ah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>How"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05D3;&#x05BC;&#x05E2;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05DE;&#x05D3;&#x05BC;&#x05D5;&#x05BC;&#x05E2; - maddu&#x0302;a&#x201B;  maddu&#x0302;a&#x201B;</b> - <i>mad-doo'-ah, mad-doo'-ah</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H4100\">H4100</a> and the passive participle of <a href=\"#/H3045\">H3045</a>; <i>what</i> (is) <i>known</i>?; that is, (by implication), (adverbially) <i>why?</i>: - how, wherefore, why."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1843\">H1843</a>, <a href=\"#/H1844\">H1844</a>, <a href=\"#/H1845\">H1845</a>, <a href=\"#/H1847\">H1847</a>, <a href=\"#/H3037\">H3037</a>, <a href=\"#/H3043\">H3043</a>, <a href=\"#/H3045\">H3045</a>, <a href=\"#/H3047\">H3047</a>, <a href=\"#/H3048\">H3048</a>, <a href=\"#/H3049\">H3049</a>, <a href=\"#/H4093\">H4093</a>, <a href=\"#/H4129\">H4129</a>, <a href=\"#/H4130\">H4130</a>"}]}